Description: The war between Luffy and Caesar Clown rages on while a deadly gas threatens the Straw Hat crew.
Title: ONE PIECE, VOL. 70
Author: Eiichiro Oda

Description: Rin Okumura joined an exorcist academy to learn how to control his demonic powers, but will his newfound knowledge ultimately help or hurt him?
Title: BLUE EXORCIST, VOL. 11
Author: Kazue Kato

Description: Ruby and Sapphire take center stage in this adventure based on the video game series.
Title: POKÉMON ADVENTURES, VOL. 21
Author: Hidenori Kusaka and Satoshi Yamamoto
Contributor: by Hidenori Kusaka and Satoshi Yamamoto

Description: In the final volume of this supernatural series, Misao is about to give birth to a demon child that would result in her own death. Can she and Kyo find a way to avoid her tragic fate?
Title: BLACK BIRD, VOL. 18
Author: Kanoko Sakurakouji

Description: The son of a notorious gangster gets caught in a love triangle with his childhood sweetheart and the daughter of his father’s rival.
Title: NISEKOI: FALSE LOVE, VOL. 2
Author: Naoshi Komi

Description: A small town is thrown into turmoil when a woman is found dead near a tunnel rumored to be the home of a mysterious creature.
Title: NIJIGAHARA HOLOGRAPH
Author: Inio Asano Inio

Description: Maron Kusakabe is a high school student by day and an art thief by night. But she only steals paintings that contain demons in order to seal them inside before they devour human hearts!
Title: PHANTOM THIEF JEANNE, VOL. 1
Author: Arina Tanemura

Description: Kaya Satozuka is reassigned to be the secretary for her company’s director, Kyohei Touma. There is only one problem: he’s a vampire!
Title: MIDNIGHT SECRETARY, VOL. 4
Author: Tomu Ohmi

Description: Dragon slayers wage a fierce battle during the fourth day of the Grand Magic Games.
Title: FAIRY TAIL, VOL. 35
Author: Hiro Mashima

Description: Is this the end of humanity? It sure looks that way when what is left of mankind must go into hiding to escape the giant humanoids known as the Titans.
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN, VOL. 1
Author: Hajime Isayama
